      <item>
        <title>MassFX simulations in Half-Life 2?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[JeffMOD]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I don’t have any links for you, (Sorry) but I would look for an SMD exporter for 3DS Max and save the simulation as an animation SMD. Also, be sure that you don’t have too many pieces of debris, as I think the bone limit for models is 256, meaning you could only have 256 separate parts max.<br>
EDIT: I do have <a href="https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/3ds_Max" data-bbcode="true" rel="nofollow noopener">links</a> <a href="https://www.chaosincarnate.net/cannonfodder/3dsmax.php" data-bbcode="true" rel="nofollow noopener">now</a>.</p>
